                                <td width="95%" style="padding-top:15px;text-align: justify;">Intimation and consent regarding modification of Development Plan and Sanctioned plans with respect to the Project <strong>“MAHENDRA AARYA”</strong> situated at Sy.Nos.6/1, 8/4, 9/2, 10/1, 12/1 and 13, Andapura Village, Attibele Hobli, Anekal Taluk, Bengaluru.</td>
